#include<iostream>
#include<cstdio>
#include<algorithm>
using namespace std;
int n,m,a[10010];
int main(){
    scanf("%d%d",&n,&m);
    for(int i=1;i<=n;i++)
        scanf("%d",&a[i]);
    while(m--)
        next_permutation(a+1,a+1+n);
    for(int i=1;i<=n;i++)
        printf("%d ",a[i]);
    return 0;
}
